name: 彌敦道
description:
Nathan Road, Shot by me in Hong Kong in March 2015 1540x1540 pixels / JPEG 

After a cloudy Sunday, which I spent at Repulse Bay, on my way home on the iconic Double Decker bus at Kowloon Side it started to rain. 

I love the mood of rainy and darkish Hong Kong, it is so colorful, beautiful and chill to me.
